title: Garmin City Navigator Europe NT 2014.20 Unlocked
description:
Garmin City Navigator Europe NT 2014.20 Unlocked


Navigate the streets with confidence. This product provides detailed road maps 
and points of interest for your device, so you can navigate with exact, turn-by-turn 
directions to any address or intersection.

Gives turn-by-turn directions on compatible devices.

Enhances pronunciation for compatible devices that speak street names 
(example: "Turn right on Main Street").

Includes navigational features, such as turn restrictions, roundabout guidance 
and speed categories.

Contains traffic data for compatible devices that use traffic receivers.




HOW TO: just copy the gmapsupp.img to a Garmin folder on your SD-card


And NO its not a fake, its the leaked latest unreleased version
